(216, 35, 'JESSICA WHITNEY', 'Any updates on this ticket? It has been a month since my follow up email and over two weeks since the last response I received regarding the 2nd order in the ticket.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n03/27/2013 Message:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you for your assistance, but what about the one from 03/15/2013 for 15% of 54.95? Shouldn\'t it be showing as pending as well? All is I see is the $24.90 pending which was the 15% of the $166.00 03/09/2013 purchase. I just want to confirm how long it takes for it to show before I submit a ticket as it seems this merchant has issues with reporting cashback (not just on your site) as I have experienced this in the past through another cashback site with only <a href=\"http://dermstore.com\">dermstore.com</a>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFrom original ticket:<br />\r\nI made another purchase today on <a href=\"http://Dermstore.com\">Dermstore.com</a> and linked from your site this time as well to also get the 15% cashback.<br />\r\nORDER CONFIRMATION NUMBER IS: 17998983<br />\r\nOrder Total $54.95', '2013-04-30 22:07:46', '', 0, NULL, '0'),
(217, 72, 'Admin', 'hi Logan, <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanks for your reply. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat I can do at this point is check with a lawyer in order to confirm this information.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease, be aware the relation between us and these companies are different from what is in this article. We are giving you a reward for shopping through us. The company is NOT directly nor indirectly paying you as a customer an adjustment in price (if you buy an item from the same store through a review website, they will earn the same commission but they would keep it for themselves). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nStore pays us a sale commission (marketing commission), that we are sharing it back with the user. The store is not running a promotion nor are we claiming they are. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAgain, in order to avoid any doubt, I will check with a lawyer and provide them a copy of our agreement with both the company and the third party. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI will keep you updated. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2013-05-01 21:15:40', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
