(934, 290, 'Admin', 'hi Konstantin,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am sorry. VitaCost did respond below is their respond : <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDate Resolved: 11-10-2013<br />\r\nResolution: Auto-Resolved <br />\r\n<br />\r\nComments:<br />\r\nDenied : Transaction Referred by Another Affiliate<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt seems you have reached to VitaCost through another affiliate partner. You probably visited them any day before that date (cookies tracking can stay for even months), we usually recommend for our user to keep one browser for online shopping, or clear their cookies. If you visited VitaCost through another website, they get granted the commission.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2013-11-20 05:42:31', '', 1, '1', '1'),
