(936, 297, 'Admin', 'hi Doris, <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe 20% is applicable for any phone below $199.99.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs of the phone offer, i went to Straight Talk Website, it shows the phone + the unlimited bundle for $144.99 (Not sure how does that breaks down). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nOffers usually are the sales prices which mean you shall be able to see that price on their site without any promo code. It could be an offer that got expired ( coupons and offers gets updated every 12 hours ).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI also checked this offer, and its expiration date show it is going on until end of 2013. I would recommend to go to straight talk website and check the price of the phone (as the final price will be the one displayed on their site).<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2013-11-22 06:24:25', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
(937, 290, 'Admin', 'hi Konstantin,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou don\'t need to register with another website for the other site to get the commission. If you visited another website that is affiliate partner of VitaCost, and clicked on the link to VitaCost website, they will still get that commission from VitaCost. It can be a review site, product link, or even a coupon site. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI have attached to my response a screen shot of the VitaCost response. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease, be aware that once you click on affiliate link, the tracking information for that website can last for month (In your case, you/ or any of the people have access to your computer with the same account did click on an affiliate link within 7 days prior to the purchase and your cookies wasn\'t cleared prior to make the purchase at our website which means your browser tracked the sale back to the other site).<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2013-11-22 06:44:33', '295#VitaCost-Missing-Transaction.png,', 1, NULL, '1'),
