(1204, 397, 'Admin', 'hi Maria,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFirst, welcome to Panda CashBack it is pleasure to have you on our website. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs of AliExpress, please don\'t worry about the transaction not being posted yet, unlike other sites, AliExpress don\'t usually post the transaction immediately, they wait for the transaction to be completed ( item received and feedback provided  ). We get bunch of transactions from AliExpress at a time and not all of them on the date of the event. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nrest assure the transaction rebate will be paid even if aliexpress failed to post the transaction. Please provide them enough time. If you don\'t see the transaction by the end of the month, let me know and i will add the rebate manually.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Admin<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2014-03-02 14:03:31', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
(1205, 391, 'Admin', 'Thank you Logan, <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs of your W-9 we destroyed all the W-9 papers for users who earn rebate only. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur first confirmation with IRS, they mentioned we required to collect the information and send 1099 to any user who make over $600 in a single year. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnother user contacted me and assured this must be an error as the rebate is form of a discount and it could be an error by the IRS agent, We went through a long process trying to confirm if that is true or wrong, including visiting the IRS office in person, contacted more than one specialist and we finally came to the conclusion ( after reaching out the department in the IRS who specialized in 1099 form only that we should issue the form only for those who providing us a service ( users who earning from referral qualifies, but that is not the case with users who earn rebates ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI do apologize for that issue, apparently the first agent we got in touch with didn\'t understand the nature of our website and assumed this is more of prizes we giving to the users / rewards and not a way of reducing the actual price of the item. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI have verified your account, if you have any question, please don\'t hesitate into contacting us. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Admin<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2014-03-02 14:10:45', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
