(1421, 452, 'Admin', 'According to Agoda, <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThese transactions were accredited to another publisher. I am sorry for how long this took them to respond. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat this mean you have reached their website through another affiliate partner ( Agoda do accredited only one publisher per transaction ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe tracking doesn\'t take place by us or Agoda, but by a 3rd party who look into cookies. Since they tracked it back to another publisher, Agoda have to honor the other publisher.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn order to avoid this issue on the future, we recommend you to use a separate browser when you shop through us. ( or clear you cookies prior to visiting our website). This way if you clicked on another website to reach to Agoda couple of a days or a month ago, the commission is tracked back to us ).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2014-05-12 21:54:58', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
