(1765, 580, 'Admin', 'hi Christopher,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease, be aware of the following, Hotwire reported to us this transaction as an airline ticket ( air line ticket has different commission rate as stated on the store page). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe pending transaction is the assumed rebate not the final rebate ( it get updated upon the commission credited from the retailer (For example, if used coupon at a retailer the initial transaction may not display the actual amount but the amount prior the discount, the store update that prior to grant us the commission ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf this is a mistake, we will be more than glad to updated it and fix it.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease, provide us with the hotwire transaction information. What type of purchase was it ? if you can provide us the confirmation email of hotwire that will be really helpful. I will reach to hotwire upon your response. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSorry for inconvenience.<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2015-07-02 02:10:18', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
