(1940, 663, 'Admin', 'hi Yu, <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanks for your question, <br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 - As far as BookingBuddy they are an affiliate of the online retailers ( just as Panda CashBack is ).E.g. Orbitz, both we and BookingBuddy are affiliate of the company, if you use BookingBuddy , who have their affiliate program they would share part of the commission with us ( which we giving it back to you. If you go through Panda CashBack to Orbitz, you are sharing the commission that Orbitz give us directly which tend to be higher. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n2 - BookingBuddy doesn\'t share the commission % with us, all we know is that they will be giving us 27% of the commission, how much that commission can\'t be exact % because they are aggregating multiple travel sites each one with different commission structure. All I can say 27% of the commission would be definitely lower than the rebate we give u directly, because we give you 50% - 100% of the commission, sometimes even higher. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n3- Please, check the BookingBuddy page, we write any restriction about a store in that section which highlight what they offering is a percentage of a commission and not of the total purchase unlike majority of travel sites. For example if we giving back 3% on Orbitz that mean of your total payment. Also, if you go directly through BookingBuddy, they wouldn\'t give you any cashback ( they are a comparison site for travel sites ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\n4- You mentioned that the purchases were for airfares, Airline tickets rebate is one of the lowers ( hotel, cars, and packages tend to be higher ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am not aware of what purchase you made at bookingbuddy because they don\'t share that with us, but if you willing to share more detail like how much you spent, at what site, and they type of purchase, i can tell you what to expect if you shopping using Panda CashBack at Expedia, Orbitz, or any other travel website ( and show you how significantly higher the cashback would be ). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease, let me know if there is anything I can assist you with. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI will contact BookingBuddy affiliate manager and ask them for a better structure as I can see even with us trying to do our best explaining it, it still confusing compare to any other travel site we partnered with so far.<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPanda CashBack Support<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pandacashback.com\">www.pandacashback.com</a><br />\n', '2016-02-16 17:57:35', '', 1, NULL, '1'),
