(3024, 1155, 'Trisha Lumalang', 'Hi Clayton,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI\'m very sorry for the late response, we\'ve faced some issues within our management that resulted to the complete change of staffs. We\'re now answering each and every tickets.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur system automatically updates and confirms cashback as soon as the stores closed the transactions and displays the corresponding amount based on our cashback offer. Because of this, we don\'t have control on the amount being reflected on your account. We\'ve checked and verified each and every transactions you had for KMART, for your withdrawal request amount, but it shows that all of your transactions are ZERO commissions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe haven\'t updated yet your account since we\'re checking all of your transactions with kmart regarding their Zero commission.but due to this issue, your request for withdrawal is declined.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have any concerns please feel free to message us. Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nTrisha<br />\n', '2018-07-04 03:21:11', '', 17, NULL, '0'),
(3025, 1151, 'Trisha Lumalang', 'Hi David,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe\'re sorry to hear that. Our system automatically confirms and approve cashback that are closed by the stores and reflects the amount on your account based on what is in our system. Due to this, we don\'t have control on the amount being reflected on your account.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChange of cashback has two possible reasons, one is that if we verified the transaction and checked the amount paid by the store. Second is that, during the processing of your transaction, the store changed their commission offer. In your case, from 6%, their commission offer drops to 1%, that\'s why your cashback changed. And we also checked the amount of your purchase, which is only $493.63 not $632.12.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI have attached here a screenshot of your transaction in <a href=\"http://BannerBuzz.ca\">BannerBuzz.ca</a>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have any more questions please feel free to message us. Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nTrisha<br />\n', '2018-07-04 03:38:43', '768#buzzer.JPG,', 17, NULL, '1'),
