(88, 'BPZ-S8H-W6VG', 'Elena Rozenberg', 'elenaroz9@gmail.com', 1, '2', 'I did not get my cash back', 'April 28 I improved in agent my order in store Modnique. I went to the store Modnique through your website. You promise 14% cash back from this store. Where\'s my cash back?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDear Elena,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you for purchasing at <a href=\"http://Modnique.com\">Modnique.com</a>. You will receive tracking information as soon as your package is sent out. You may also find the shipment update in \'My Account\' section of <a href=\"http://Modnique.com\">Modnique.com</a>.<br />\r\nHere is your purchase information:<br />\r\nBilling Address:<br />\r\nMoshav Amnon,127<br />\r\nMoshav Amnon<br />\r\nD.N.Drom Golan 12935 IL<br />\r\nShipping Address:<br />\r\nMoshav Amnon,127<br />\r\nMoshav Amnon<br />\r\nD.N.Drom Golan 12935 IL<br />\r\n	<br />\r\nSubtotal:<br />\r\n	55.00<br />\r\nTax:<br />\r\n	0.00<br />\r\nShipping:<br />\r\n	15.98<br />\r\nStore Credit:<br />\r\n	70.98<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\nTotal Price:<br />\r\n	0.00<br />\r\n	<br />\r\nOrder Number:<br />\r\n	174712048<br />\r\nShipping Method:<br />\r\n	International Expedited Parcel<br />\r\nEstimated Delivery:<br />\r\n	05/09/2013<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease keep in mind that most packages will be shipped 10-17 days after we received your order. They will then be delivered by FedEx or USPS in 1-8 business days to most continental US destinations (a few days longer for HI, AK, military and territorial addresses).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhy delay shipments by 10-17 days? We order your items directly from designers after the sale event ends. This greatly reduces costs and we extend these savings directly to you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCanadian and Australian orders will be delivered by your local post office or FedEx. Delivery usually takes 3 to 8 business days.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOrders to other countries will be delivered by your local post office, Aramex, or FedEx. Delivery times v