(605, 'GD2-M7A-YS6Q', 'Ivan', 'ivanserrano217@gmail.com', 1, '3', 'contributing to pandacashback.com', 'Hi <a href=\"http://pandacashback.com\">pandacashback.com</a>,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMy name is Ivan Serrano and I am freelance business/marketing journalist and finance enthusiast. I just wanted to say that <a href=\"http://pandacashback.com\">pandacashback.com</a> offers great information and advice about budgeting and savings. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI know it has not been solicited, but I believe that with my knowledge in writing and my passion for business, my writings would fit really well with your website.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBelow are some examples of my work so you can check out my contributions on business blogs and style.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.businessrevieweurope.eu/marketing/403/5-Reasons-to-Market-on-Instagram\">www.businessrevieweurope.eu/marketing/403/5-Reasons-to-Market-on-Instagram</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://understandingecommerce.com/2015/04/nurturing-the-sales-funnel-using-social-media\">understandingecommerce.com/2015/04/nurturing-the-sales-funnel-using-social-media</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.powtoon.com/blog/digital-marketing-2015/\">www.powtoon.com/blog/digital-marketing-2015/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you’re interested at all, I could write unique pieces for your website and could even send you some topics once I hear back from you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlthough personal finance is a broad topic, if this is something you’re interested in, I can come up with a more narrow scope. I am also open to any ideas you may have if this isn’t a good fit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBy the way, I\'m not looking for any monetary compensation for this, I just want to expand my portfolio and exposure as a writer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLooking forward to hearing from you!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBest,<br />\r\nIvan Serrano', '2015-09-14 16:58:28', '2015-09-26 05:55:29', '162.158.93.197', NULL, '3', 1, '06:33:28', '1', 1, '0', '0', '',