(706, 'XEB-P28-5LEL', 'Grigoriy', 'admin@bomz.org', 1, '3', 'Cooperation offer', 'Hi, i am the author of russian cashback rating project <a href=\"http://cashback2.ru\">cashback2.ru</a> <br />\r\nI want to connect your service (is free) to our cashback rating &amp; comparison site. <br />\r\nNeed automatic export of shops &amp; cashbacks from your site in CSV or TEXT format like this:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLink toshop (sample, use text: http://amazon.com); <br />\r\nCash Back amount (if it 7.2%, use number: 7.2); <br />\r\nCashback amount from (sample, use number: 5.5); <br />\r\nCashback amount to (sample, use number: 9.2); <br />\r\nFixed amount (if it 2USD back, use number: 2); <br />\r\ncurrency (sample, text:USD); <br />\r\nlink to shop info page in your site; <br />\r\ntime to wait cashback (sample, text: 45-90 days); <br />\r\nother info (sample, text: promocode, short cashback info etc..)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn real export, info is like this (one line - one shop):<br />\r\n<br />\r\namazon.com;7.5;5.5;9.2;350;RUB;http://mycashbackservice.xx/magaz-info/;45-90 days;use promo code BONUS +1% for you<br />\r\namazon2.com;7.5;5.5;9.2;350;RUB;http://mycashbackservice.xx/magaz-info/;45-90 days;use promo code BONUS +1% for you<br />\r\namazon3.com;7.5;5.5;9.2;350;RUB;http://mycashbackservice.xx/magaz-info/;45-90 days;use promo code BONUS +1% for you<br />\r\namazon4.com;7.5;5.5;9.2;350;RUB;http://mycashbackservice.xx/magaz-info/;45-90 days;use promo code BONUS +1% for you<br />\r\namazon5.com;7.5;5.5;9.2;350;RUB;http://mycashbackservice.xx/magaz-info/;45-90 days;use promo code BONUS +1% for you<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSorry for my bad english, if you have questions, you can ask me, thanks for cooperation.', '2016-05-07 12:54:53', '2016-08-07 05:54:14', '176.37.63.44', NULL, '3', 1, '00:10:19', '1', 1, '0', '0', '', '', '<li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-07 13:54:53 submitted by Grigoriy</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-07 13:54:53 automatically assigned to Admin (Admin)</l