(707, 'L6H-21V-MW9P', 'Alexander Santiago', 'alancms@gmail.com', 1, '1', 'No pending cashback', 'I\'ve shopped at Ebay and completed a purchase but there is no pending cashback? Please check my account, I would have shopped for more (at least 4 moe times) but since there is no pending cashback, I chose ebates to shop at eBay. Please check my account thanks.', '2016-05-08 09:01:27', '2016-05-09 03:59:56', '24.4.147.26', NULL, '3', 1, '00:13:45', '1', 1, '0', '0', '', '', '<li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-08 10:01:27 submitted by Alexander Santiago</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-08 10:01:27 automatically assigned to Admin (Admin)</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-08 23:59:56 closed by Admin (Admin)</li>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
