(710, '48R-GLR-3AUV', 'Dexter Josephs', 'saverbates@mail.com', 1, '1', 'cj.com affiliate', 'I have applied to become a partner on <a href=\"http://cj.com\">cj.com</a> and kindly asking you to accept my offer<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGoalur is a new and innovative platform that is currently being developed. However there are some content necessary to ensure continual growth for the company. We would like to create a partnership with you so that on the web page <a href=\"http://goalur.com\">goalur.com</a> user can have access to your sites with a link through us as a portal. It would be of some significance to generate massive advertising and sales for your goods and services. We are engaged to a demand of millions of users to our site that extends as customers to a company such as yours and also goalur is a hardworking organization to enhance business flow with direct planning to influence the audience to your business. Some applications include press releases, seo marketing, social media and banner ads. If we can accomplish these statistics it would be ideal not only for now but also for future expansion of your business enterprise.', '2016-05-10 22:04:04', '2016-05-20 13:41:01', '108.75.201.241', NULL, '3', 1, '00:03:23', '1', 1, '0', '0', '', '', '<li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-10 23:04:04 submitted by Dexter Josephs</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-10 23:04:04 automatically assigned to Michelle (Sasha27)</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-12 21:57:23 assigned to Admin (Admin) by Admin (Admin)</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-20 09:41:01 closed by (automatically)</li>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
