(718, '9A2-LTD-U883', 'Kai Ieda', 'kai.ieda@linkshare.com', 1, '1', 'Invitation to Rakuten Linkshare Japan', 'This is Kai Ieda from Rakuten Linkshare Japan. <br />\r\nHope this email finds you well. <br />\r\n <br />\r\nI would like to introduce you our Japanese affiliate network and hope that you will consider joining us.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nRakuten Linkshare has branch offices located worldwide and I currently represent the Tokyo office: Linkshare Japan K.K. You might not be familiar with us, but we have an exclusive partnership with a lot of well-known Japanese merchants, such as Rakuten group services, DHC, Sony, Fujitsu, NEC, etc., who are highly pleased with our service and support. As a result, we have been awarded as the No.1 ASP in Japan for 6 consecutive years.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nPlease refer to the link below to learn more about us.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://jp.linkshare.com/\">jp.linkshare.com/</a> <br />\r\n <br />\r\nWhile providing Japanese partners with our service locally, we also want to help them reach overseas markets and make their unique products more easily available to international shoppers. To do that, we are seeking to expand our service by letting overseas publishers join our network. Our main target is China and if your target users are also Chinese or living in China, I think that we could be a good match and there is an opportunity there for us to work together since Chinese shoppers can really be attracted by Japanese products.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nPlease do not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions.<br />\r\nWe are looking forward to hearing back from you. <br />\r\n <br />\r\nBest regards,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKai Ieda', '2016-05-19 01:45:42', '2018-10-12 08:17:03', '133.237.7.82', NULL, '1', 1, '00:44:39', '0', 1, '0', '0', '554#How-to-join-linkshare-service.pdf,', '', '<li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-19 02:45:42 submitted by Kai Ieda</li><li class=\"smaller\">On 2016-05-19 02:45:42 automatically assigned to Michelle (Sas